{"tid":1438694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋聞追Click】IT人研發AI認警察程式 竟涉教唆謀殺被捕可囚終身","createTime":"2019-08-10T00:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:44:24.000Z","uid":272569,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2c62d6e2a6dd90a47e9d068554e7f71f75cd49","tid":1438694,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:09:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59911383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59911383&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=c9930711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59911383&h=f6401b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59911383</a><br />\n<br />\n警方由6月9日至今拘捕逾420人，IT人Colin涉及最重罪的「串謀或教唆謀殺」，最高刑罰可囚終身監禁，他的故事登上《紐約時報》。Colin接受《蘋果》訪問稱，自己只是研發一個人工智能辨認警察程式，希望反制警員拒絕出示委任證。程式在內部測試階段時，他已被警察拘捕。他澄清沒有教唆殺警意圖，批評警方以重罪拘捕是白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\nColin憶述，7月18日中午他外出買飯，在商場被警員拘捕並按倒在地下，其後被帶到停車場一架七人私家車內。警員拉上窗簾後摑打其臉部，曾喝罵「清醒呀！清醒呀！清唔清醒呀！」更有警員用拳頭毆打他的肋骨位置。他指，警員強行撐開他的眼瞼，嘗試以面容辨識解鎖其手機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebf0eaa6a5e6b3e3aae4b3c8b127d59e6963703","tid":1438694,"uid":110008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d47b3bfc2b14f81dcf13c8def199510c087b89a","tid":1438694,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:11:51.000Z","msg":"黑警老屈"},{"pid":"3aaa8aa77471a8d2ea3a1dbc115a391bdfe7d798","tid":1438694,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"小心電話、電腦IP<br />\nTelegram保護好個人資料<br />\n<br />\n推行動post呀<br />\n<br />\n【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2303d35381cb64dafd27f8c9dddbaf49c7f469f0","tid":1438694,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:12:19.000Z","msg":"Cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3603c106b44b9af8ed96348f12899a2224ade3ac","tid":1438694,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:12:53.000Z","msg":"痴線咁都得"},{"pid":"a6ea6c145d15e0dd0a2953a0517a64ec949b92bc","tid":1438694,"uid":176508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:13:31.000Z","msg":"救巴救巴救巴"},{"pid":"de441766d94a33d3d7c85ccad1d18fc8ca3023e5","tid":1438694,"uid":28685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"一定要推"},{"pid":"8b10f8bd131550210c0485ebde16b02c0e64c11e","tid":1438694,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"文宣商戰：撐「五大訴求、缺一不可」良心認證標誌店舖消費推廣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1cd02a006654244e4dba7510661125c8772e040b","tid":1438694,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:30:16.000Z","msg":"黑警"},{"pid":"86d6942e0454224eb5d44979682f3a852394dfde","tid":1438694,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:37:33.000Z","msg":"🐕<br />\n冇野講<br />\n好撚嬲"},{"pid":"5fbde270afb31a619eccfa38f3c9fe61ad428814","tid":1438694,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:38:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4a052355d436f76181ac7ab312720151e7194